                        <span class="data-driven-title desc_short">Little Lions Preschool</span>
                        <span class="desc_long">The Little Lions Preschool program offers a play-based kindergarten readiness preschool curriculum for 3 and 4 year olds. It teaches intellectual, social and emotional development, language skills, positive self-concepts and self-expression through large and small group learning. Children explore, experiment and engage in themed activities that are planned for a range of levels in each of the developmental domains.

We are accepting enrollments for the 2019-20 school year. Call 517.852.9468 ext. 4405 to make an appointment.</span>
